OL,3,CHope on the menu at cafe staffed by
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse survivors
OL,6,FSurvivors of domestic violence are
OL,7,Fstarting a new chapter of their lives
OL,8,Fat a cafe in Londonderry.
OL,10,FThe Family Justice Centre was set up
OL,11,Fnot just to help survivors of abuse
OL,12,Fnavigate the judicial system, but also
OL,13,Fto give them refuge, advice and skills.
OL,15,FWomen recovering from violent
OL,16,Frelationships say working at Cafe
OL,17,FCentral has given them the skills they
OL,18,Fneed to succeed.
