OL,6,FUTV has been documenting the issue of
OL,7,Fviolence against women and girls in a
OL,8,Fseries of special reports.
OL,10,FThe Family Justice Centre is just one
OL,11,Fof many services offering a fresh
OL,12,Fapproach to supporting survivors.
OL,14,FMary is one of the members of staff at
OL,15,Fthe cafe.
OL,17,FShe said: "It is very important
OL,18,Fbecause it helps rebuild your life
OL,19,Fafter all you have been through and
OL,20,Fwhat life has thrown at you. "
