OL,4,Cdomestic abuse survivors
OL,6,FThe women who work at the cafe have
OL,7,Fgraduated from a hospitality academy
OL,8,Frun by Foyle Women's Aid, with all
OL,9,Fprofits put back into the organisation.
OL,11,FSarah Quinn from Foyle Women's Aid
OL,12,Fsaid: "It is all about confidence. It
OL,13,Fis about building them back up and
OL,14,Fgiving the women an opportunity, maybe
OL,15,Ftrying something new.
