OL,6,F"Some women would have come through
OL,7,Fthe hospitality academy with maybe not
OL,8,Fmuch of an interest in catering or
OL,9,Fworking in a cafe, but now they
OL,10,Fabsolutely love it and they are
OL,11,Fthriving.
OL,13,F"For us, it is about the opportunities
OL,14,Fthat it can bring for them in their
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,17,FKaren has found a sense of community
OL,18,Fworking in the cafe.
