OL,6,F"We were all in the same boat and we
OL,7,Fall connected, it was so lovely", she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"It gave us an opportunity to get back
OL,11,Fout to work. I was jumping through all
OL,12,Fthe hoops that were there and
OL,13,Favailable to me to help get me back
OL,14,Fout to society again."
OL,16,FThe Family Justice Centre offers a
OL,17,F'one stop shop' for survivors. The
OL,18,Finnovative approach was imported from
OL,19,FAmerica by Marie Brown, CEO of Foyle
OL,20,FWomen's Aid.
