OL,6,FIt is the only centre of its kind in
OL,7,Fthe UK or Ireland with integrated
OL,8,Fservices, including a court witness
OL,9,Fsuite.
OL,11,FThe room could eventually spare
OL,12,Fvictims the trauma of facing abusers
OL,13,Fin court by enabling witnesses to give
OL,14,Fevidence remotely.
OL,16,F"We know that where remote court
OL,17,Fevidence is used, there are good
OL,18,Fconviction rates," Marie said.
