OL,6,FHowever, victims are already helped
OL,7,Fhere on their journeys towards
OL,8,Fprosecutions.
OL,10,FOne woman who survived decades of
OL,11,Fabuse, told UTV: "The support that you
OL,12,Fget here helps you to stay the course.
OL,14,F"There's everything to help you to
OL,15,Fcontinue through and help you get to
OL,16,Fthe end. To get the outcome you
OL,17,Fdeserve, to be safe and to have him
OL,18,Fout of your life. "
OL,20,F'Camp Hope' is another idea that has
OL,21,Ftravelled across the Atlantic.
